divs: Sighting DetailsHi, while taking a sequence of around 8 pictures including short 2 minute video, a mass or small dark cloud was in sequential pictures; @4:09, 4;09, 4:09, 4:10! Equals 4 sequential black small cloulds in front of sun. With two vey small black clouds to the right. A third tiny! Note. The fifth 4:10 picture was completely void of all three black cloud like entities. Then i ran a video 2 minutes. @4:11 to 4:12 No small black clouds at all in two minutes. The 6th picture at 4:14 void of cloud like mass in center of lower sun , now has an oval white orb! ! (First oval shaped i've photgrahed ) At right area where cloud mass was. Question. Is there a relationship of the cloud like dark spot , missing cloud, followed by an oval white orb total time less than 5 minutes from cloud mass to void to oval orb? Just observing the orb phenominon. G.A. whittier
